Post.create(title: '', content: 'Hold onto your hearts! ‚ô•Ô∏è‚ô•Ô∏è‚ô•Ô∏è‚ô•Ô∏è THE AGE OF THE QUICK FIX is here! We had a great time brewing this with Mike Murphy from LERVIG. This beer used Pils malt, wheat & flaked oats & was dry-hopped with loads of CRYO Ekuanot & Loral. Soured using our in-house lactic acid plant, this beer is sharp, fruity and lemony - think of a refreshing and hoppy limonata! So goddam crushable! Very limited quantity, so get in quick. Out W/C 13th May 6.2%, 12IBU, 9EBC Can illustration: Nanna Guldbak Graphic Design : Sammy Davis', brewery_id: b4.id)
